BT /F1 18 Tf 50 780 Td (1. AUTHENTICATION & SECURITY) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 50 750 Td (Security is our top priority. All requests must be authenticated.) Tj ET
BT /F1 14 Tf 50 710 Td (1.1 API KEYS) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 690 Td (Generate your unique developer key via the Pagume Bot dashboard.) Tj ET
